1
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:34,048
=The Glamorous Night=

2
00:01:36,552 --> 00:01:37,112
(Five Years Ago)
Alright then.

3
00:01:37,593 --> 00:01:38,856
Let's go with this bottle then.

4
00:01:38,953 --> 00:01:39,672
Well explained.

5
00:01:40,353 --> 00:01:41,272
Thank you, Fang.

6
00:01:42,633 --> 00:01:43,153
Ms. Zhao.

7
00:01:44,793 --> 00:01:45,293
Okay.

8
00:01:45,513 --> 00:01:47,953
You all have seen
the entire process now.

9
00:01:48,312 --> 00:01:51,392
Next, we'll proceed
with group practice drills, okay?

10
00:01:51,392 --> 00:01:53,512
Decide who is the sales lady
and who is the customer.

11
00:01:53,752 --> 00:01:55,752
Customers, try to act
a bit more demanding.

12
00:01:55,912 --> 00:01:56,552
- Okay.
- Okay.

13
00:01:56,552 --> 00:01:57,472
Then let's begin.

14
00:01:57,928 --> 00:01:58,552
- Okay.
- Okay.

15
00:01:58,552 --> 00:01:59,052
Come on.

16
00:01:59,624 --> 00:02:00,232
Let's team up.

17
00:02:00,232 --> 00:02:01,272
Fine, then you...

18
00:02:01,272 --> 00:02:02,552
Yes, pull this apart.

19
00:02:02,633 --> 00:02:04,153
Let's move this over there first.

20
00:02:04,353 --> 00:02:04,853
Go there.

21
00:02:05,192 --> 00:02:06,032
Don't block this.

22
00:02:07,832 --> 00:02:09,432
This batch of newcomers is promising.

23
00:02:10,473 --> 00:02:12,392
I plan to select a few
for focused development.

24
00:02:12,592 --> 00:02:13,633
Send to flagship stores.

25
00:02:15,193 --> 00:02:16,353
I'll also focus on you.

26
00:02:19,913 --> 00:02:20,753
These years,

27
00:02:21,473 --> 00:02:23,033
the sales promoter team has expanded

28
00:02:23,552 --> 00:02:24,793
and becomes more important.

29
00:02:26,233 --> 00:02:26,953
The boss approved

30
00:02:27,432 --> 00:02:28,872
a standalone Promotions Department,

31
00:02:29,793 --> 00:02:31,392
headed by a Deputy Director

32
00:02:31,848 --> 00:02:32,513
reporting to me.

33
00:02:33,073 --> 00:02:37,073
So who will be
this newly minted Deputy Director?

34
00:02:38,633 --> 00:02:39,304
Take a guess.

35
00:02:41,513 --> 00:02:42,353
Is it me?

36
00:02:45,233 --> 00:02:47,233
An email announcement
will go out early next month.

37
00:02:47,633 --> 00:02:48,712
Training will be in Paris.

38
00:02:49,073 --> 00:02:50,216
Thank you, Mr. Xu.

39
00:02:50,592 --> 00:02:51,752
I promise I'll do my best.

40
00:02:54,152 --> 00:02:55,172
Hello, everyone.

41
00:02:55,304 --> 00:02:57,992
I'm the brand promotion representative
for Gennadiy.

42
00:02:58,112 --> 00:02:59,048
(New Product Launch)
My name is Zhao Mei.

43
00:02:59,473 --> 00:03:02,536
Welcome to the Gennadiy Launch Event.

44
00:03:12,488 --> 00:03:13,832
(No More Bets)

45
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,624
(Counterattack)

46
00:03:17,710 --> 00:03:21,512
=Episode 3=
(A Cornered Rabbit)

47
00:03:36,592 --> 00:03:37,152
Hello.

48
00:03:44,152 --> 00:03:46,392
May I ask what time
do you usually finish work?

49
00:03:51,432 --> 00:03:52,073
Forget I asked.

50
00:04:00,033 --> 00:04:02,832
Actually, I am capable
of being the Sales Director.

51
00:04:08,592 --> 00:04:10,760
Look, I've been at GST
for so many years.

52
00:04:11,313 --> 00:04:12,913
I sell wine every single day.

53
00:04:13,033 --> 00:04:15,353
Every day, I think
about how to sell it better.

54
00:04:15,872 --> 00:04:17,152
I also understand management.

55
00:04:17,592 --> 00:04:19,496
The hundreds-strong
promotion team at GST

56
00:04:19,496 --> 00:04:20,712
was built up entirely by me.

57
00:04:20,712 --> 00:04:22,536
Even Xu Yuntian isn't
as good as me at this.

58
00:04:23,433 --> 00:04:25,433
If I become Sales Director,

59
00:04:25,592 --> 00:04:28,808
I can elevate the capabilities
of our entire

60
00:04:28,808 --> 00:04:29,832
sales team by a notch.

61
00:04:32,032 --> 00:04:32,592
Ms. Qi,

62
00:04:33,032 --> 00:04:33,912
believe in me.

63
00:04:34,392 --> 00:04:35,513
Give me a chance.

64
00:04:36,152 --> 00:04:38,120
I can do better than anyone else.

65
00:04:40,032 --> 00:04:41,912
I really appreciate you telling me

66
00:04:43,032 --> 00:04:43,792
your request.

67
00:04:45,832 --> 00:04:47,176
We will consider it carefully.

68
00:04:57,712 --> 00:04:58,392
Zhao Mei,

69
00:04:58,753 --> 00:04:59,592
it's time to wake up.

70
00:05:00,152 --> 00:05:00,792
Wake up.

71
00:05:01,392 --> 00:05:02,873
The sun is high. Time to get up.

72
00:05:03,592 --> 00:05:04,633
Quick, get up.

73
00:05:06,392 --> 00:05:07,032
Mom?

74
00:05:07,712 --> 00:05:09,313
Why sleep separately from Dongming?

75
00:05:11,592 --> 00:05:13,433
We're not sleeping separately.

76
00:05:13,753 --> 00:05:15,232
Why did he sleep in the guest room?

77
00:05:21,272 --> 00:05:22,193
Li Dongming.

78
00:05:22,832 --> 00:05:24,832
Don't shout at him. Let him sleep.

79
00:05:24,993 --> 00:05:26,032
I'm asking you.

80
00:05:26,032 --> 00:05:26,592
You...

81
00:05:26,912 --> 00:05:27,472
Wake up.

82
00:05:27,772 --> 00:05:29,073
- Wake up.
- What are you doing?

83
00:05:29,152 --> 00:05:30,712
- Let him sleep.
- Mom's here.

84
00:05:30,712 --> 00:05:32,392
I was asking you, not him.

85
00:05:32,392 --> 00:05:33,352
Honestly, you...

86
00:05:33,832 --> 00:05:34,332
See?

87
00:05:35,272 --> 00:05:35,993
You woke him up.

88
00:05:36,912 --> 00:05:38,032
Mom, what brings you here?

89
00:05:38,313 --> 00:05:39,232
Can't I come?

90
00:05:39,712 --> 00:05:41,113
Mom just asked me

91
00:05:41,113 --> 00:05:42,832
why we are sleeping separately.

92
00:05:44,953 --> 00:05:46,753
W-We never slept separately.

93
00:05:51,633 --> 00:05:53,272
I came back late last night.

94
00:05:53,272 --> 00:05:55,392
I slept here because I feared
I'd wake Zhao Mei up.

95
00:05:58,272 --> 00:05:59,232
That's good.

96
00:06:00,152 --> 00:06:00,652
See?

97
00:06:01,073 --> 00:06:02,193
My son woke up.

98
00:06:02,193 --> 00:06:03,073
Go back to sleep.

99
00:06:03,472 --> 00:06:04,193
Sorry about that.

100
00:06:04,193 --> 00:06:04,993
Sleep a bit longer.

101
00:06:04,993 --> 00:06:06,513
So early in the morning, honestly.

102
00:06:06,513 --> 00:06:08,968
The sun's high. Get up quickly, 'Son'.

103
00:06:14,753 --> 00:06:17,000
If you want to be a mom
so badly, have one.

104
00:06:19,832 --> 00:06:20,332
Dad.

105
00:06:21,232 --> 00:06:21,873
You get up.

106
00:06:22,513 --> 00:06:23,753
Breakfast will be ready soon.

107
00:06:23,944 --> 00:06:24,832
Dad, I won't eat.

108
00:06:24,953 --> 00:06:26,193
I have a meeting this morning.

109
00:06:27,193 --> 00:06:27,993
I'll pack it.

110
00:06:28,073 --> 00:06:29,256
What do you want for dinner?

111
00:06:29,256 --> 00:06:30,753
Your dad will cook and set it aside.

112
00:06:30,753 --> 00:06:32,296
You and Dongming can eat back home.

113
00:06:32,753 --> 00:06:34,073
I'll be working overtime tonight.

114
00:06:34,953 --> 00:06:35,816
Don't worry about me.

115
00:06:35,816 --> 00:06:36,808
I have a business trip.

116
00:06:37,272 --> 00:06:38,433
How can you live like this?

117
00:06:38,712 --> 00:06:40,673
One's on business trips,
the other work overtime.

118
00:06:40,953 --> 00:06:43,272
A married couple
shouldn't be apart all the time,

119
00:06:43,472 --> 00:06:43,972
right?

120
00:06:44,113 --> 00:06:45,433
Your relationship will suffer.

121
00:06:45,513 --> 00:06:46,193
Zhao Mei.

122
00:06:47,953 --> 00:06:48,453
Take this.

123
00:06:49,193 --> 00:06:49,832
Thanks, Dad.

124
00:06:51,753 --> 00:06:53,073
Say less.

125
00:06:53,272 --> 00:06:54,673
As family, we should speak freely.

126
00:06:55,693 --> 00:06:56,193
By the way,

127
00:06:56,193 --> 00:06:57,832
Zhao Mei, there's something
I need to ask.

128
00:06:58,193 --> 00:07:00,392
Did the harassment case online

129
00:07:00,592 --> 00:07:01,592
happen in your company?

130
00:07:02,193 --> 00:07:03,873
Yes, but she is unrelated.

131
00:07:04,073 --> 00:07:05,392
How is she unrelated?

132
00:07:05,832 --> 00:07:07,592
Wasn't that girl a sales lady?

133
00:07:07,753 --> 00:07:09,953
And isn't Zhao Mei
in charge of the sales ladies?

134
00:07:09,953 --> 00:07:11,113
What do you mean unrelated?

135
00:07:11,712 --> 00:07:12,392
Zhao Mei,

136
00:07:12,633 --> 00:07:14,193
I think your company is unreliable.

137
00:07:14,633 --> 00:07:15,392
The culture's bad.

138
00:07:15,633 --> 00:07:17,352
It's not worth
killing yourself for them.

139
00:07:17,352 --> 00:07:18,392
Just listen to me.

140
00:07:18,392 --> 00:07:19,712
Mom, how can you say that?

141
00:07:20,032 --> 00:07:21,640
You insulted her company
in front of her.

142
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,912
Would you be happy if I said
your school was terrible?

143
00:07:24,832 --> 00:07:26,760
How terrible could a school be?

144
00:07:27,232 --> 00:07:28,433
It's a place for teaching.

145
00:07:30,712 --> 00:07:31,792
Dongming, let me tell you.

146
00:07:32,073 --> 00:07:33,873
People in her company

147
00:07:34,592 --> 00:07:35,953
always go

148
00:07:35,953 --> 00:07:38,912
to bars, nightclubs,
all those seedy places.

149
00:07:39,313 --> 00:07:40,832
- Can you feel at ease?
- I can.

150
00:07:41,032 --> 00:07:43,712
- I go to bars and nightclubs often too.
- (Knowing full well I can hear,)

151
00:07:43,712 --> 00:07:45,032
(yet they're talking nonstop.)

152
00:07:46,032 --> 00:07:47,433
(It's a double act for me.)

153
00:07:47,633 --> 00:07:49,193
It's not just the bad culture.

154
00:07:49,712 --> 00:07:51,848
Just the constant late nights
and drinking alone

155
00:07:51,848 --> 00:07:52,592
is unacceptable.

156
00:07:53,032 --> 00:07:54,792
Zhao Mei will have children eventually.

157
00:07:55,193 --> 00:07:55,693
Mom.

158
00:07:56,313 --> 00:07:56,813
Dad.

159
00:07:57,313 --> 00:07:58,232
Enjoy your meal.

160
00:07:58,313 --> 00:07:59,032
I have to go.

161
00:07:59,953 --> 00:08:00,513
Dongming,

162
00:08:01,193 --> 00:08:02,592
my tire seems to have a problem.

163
00:08:02,753 --> 00:08:03,352
Take a look.

164
00:08:04,712 --> 00:08:06,313
I-I'll go change clothes.

165
00:08:06,832 --> 00:08:07,433
Wait for me.

166
00:08:15,513 --> 00:08:18,152
Step two in taking the fall
for the company today.

167
00:08:18,633 --> 00:08:20,073
Doing media interviews.

168
00:08:20,392 --> 00:08:22,920
Voluntarily shouldering the blame.

169
00:08:23,392 --> 00:08:24,633
Don't say anything unnecessary.

170
00:08:25,912 --> 00:08:26,513
I know.

171
00:08:26,873 --> 00:08:28,513
I won't take this blame for nothing.

172
00:08:30,152 --> 00:08:31,633
I've already told Qi Youlan

173
00:08:31,953 --> 00:08:33,953
that I'm aiming
for the Sales Director position.

174
00:08:34,512 --> 00:08:35,273
That's great.

175
00:08:35,592 --> 00:08:37,273
Straight to the point, declare the war.

176
00:08:38,512 --> 00:08:39,273
I'm so tired.

177
00:08:40,793 --> 00:08:42,193
Sorry for putting you through this.

178
00:08:42,752 --> 00:08:43,913
When everything is settled,

179
00:08:44,193 --> 00:08:45,872
let's find a scenic spot

180
00:08:45,872 --> 00:08:46,752
and take a vacation.

181
00:08:48,193 --> 00:08:50,792
Once I get fired,
I'll have plenty time for that.

182
00:08:50,913 --> 00:08:52,393
That day will never come.

183
00:08:53,033 --> 00:08:53,992
Which tire is broken?

184
00:08:55,393 --> 00:08:56,512
Your brain is broken.

185
00:08:57,273 --> 00:08:58,344
If I hadn't said that,

186
00:08:58,344 --> 00:09:00,273
how could I get you out
for a private talk?

187
00:09:02,632 --> 00:09:03,752
You've improved.

188
00:09:05,393 --> 00:09:06,232
Learned from you.

189
00:09:06,352 --> 00:09:07,953
- I'm leaving.
- Take care.

190
00:09:34,953 --> 00:09:35,472
Ms. Zhao,

191
00:09:35,872 --> 00:09:37,193
sales just complained,

192
00:09:37,193 --> 00:09:38,913
saying these freebies all have issues,

193
00:09:39,153 --> 00:09:40,153
straws all broken.

194
00:09:41,273 --> 00:09:42,673
- Which team?
- Tang Lide's.

195
00:09:51,712 --> 00:09:52,212
Straws?

196
00:09:57,433 --> 00:09:58,872
These aren't broken.

197
00:09:59,153 --> 00:10:02,352
- He's tossing the blame at us again.
- (I took the fall for Xu Yuntian.)

198
00:10:02,352 --> 00:10:04,793
(Now every nobody thinks
they can pin it on me.)

199
00:10:05,033 --> 00:10:05,533
(No way.)

200
00:10:05,872 --> 00:10:07,472
(I need to show them what's what.)

201
00:10:08,832 --> 00:10:09,393
Mid-lane!

202
00:10:09,393 --> 00:10:10,512
Someone's backdooring!

203
00:10:11,232 --> 00:10:12,433
Wait! I'll go!

204
00:10:12,752 --> 00:10:14,600
Are elementary kids playing
on weekdays now?

205
00:10:18,112 --> 00:10:19,872
You're...

206
00:10:19,872 --> 00:10:20,512
Tong.

207
00:10:20,616 --> 00:10:21,608
Yes, Tong.

208
00:10:22,232 --> 00:10:23,352
What brings you here?

209
00:10:24,512 --> 00:10:25,512
Didn't you complain

210
00:10:25,512 --> 00:10:27,393
that our straw cups here are all broken?

211
00:10:28,752 --> 00:10:29,673
These are all new.

212
00:10:30,752 --> 00:10:31,872
Ms. Zhao said

213
00:10:32,112 --> 00:10:34,673
you can step on them however you want.

214
00:10:35,313 --> 00:10:36,273
Once break, it's on us.

215
00:10:37,992 --> 00:10:39,033
What are you, an Aries?

216
00:10:40,673 --> 00:10:41,193
Mao,

217
00:10:41,673 --> 00:10:43,953
did promotions find
out we damaged the freebies?

218
00:10:44,112 --> 00:10:44,673
What then?

219
00:10:44,913 --> 00:10:46,033
So what if they found out?

220
00:10:46,033 --> 00:10:46,712
What can she do?

221
00:10:48,872 --> 00:10:49,592
Just step for fun.

222
00:10:50,712 --> 00:10:53,273
Pull all the sales data
from the past three years.

223
00:10:53,872 --> 00:10:55,393
Tang Lide's, Dong Yue's.

224
00:10:55,512 --> 00:10:56,472
And Xu's own data.

225
00:10:57,712 --> 00:10:59,112
And the direct-operated stores.

226
00:10:59,752 --> 00:11:01,632
Also include
the annual analysis reports.

227
00:11:02,112 --> 00:11:03,232
Compile everything.

228
00:11:05,872 --> 00:11:06,872
Past years are okay.

229
00:11:07,632 --> 00:11:08,968
As for this year's,

230
00:11:09,393 --> 00:11:10,673
I need to ask sales for it.

231
00:11:10,673 --> 00:11:11,913
Then go ask them for it.

232
00:11:12,393 --> 00:11:13,472
Send it to their assistant

233
00:11:13,992 --> 00:11:15,688
and copy all relevant parties.

234
00:11:16,752 --> 00:11:17,352
Ms. Zhao,

235
00:11:18,112 --> 00:11:19,273
are you planning to...

236
00:11:22,232 --> 00:11:24,273
I heard you want to be Sales Director.

237
00:11:24,752 --> 00:11:26,073
I thought it was just a rumor.

238
00:11:26,992 --> 00:11:27,512
It's true?

239
00:11:30,992 --> 00:11:31,784
You heard?

240
00:11:33,512 --> 00:11:34,632
From many people?

241
00:11:35,393 --> 00:11:36,520
Not that many.

242
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,112
Just some in administration.

243
00:11:42,872 --> 00:11:43,872
Just want to try.

244
00:11:46,472 --> 00:11:47,688
I'll support you with my life.

245
00:11:48,512 --> 00:11:49,960
I'll go organize the materials now.

246
00:11:51,992 --> 00:11:52,492
By the way,

247
00:11:53,512 --> 00:11:55,720
I actually have a lot of dirt
on those sales guys.

248
00:11:56,153 --> 00:11:57,128
Want me to dig that up?

249
00:11:58,872 --> 00:12:00,313
Why more enthusiastic than me?

250
00:12:00,913 --> 00:12:02,112
You're our boss.

251
00:12:02,273 --> 00:12:04,553
If you succeed, we all succeed.

252
00:12:05,553 --> 00:12:06,112
Go to work.

253
00:12:07,153 --> 00:12:08,953
Ask the girls under you

254
00:12:09,592 --> 00:12:11,193
if Xu Yuntian ever harassed them.

255
00:12:11,752 --> 00:12:14,073
Intentionally, unintentionally,
accidentally, any kind.

256
00:12:14,992 --> 00:12:17,433
Photos or videos would be best.

257
00:12:17,512 --> 00:12:18,472
Have them submit it all.

258
00:12:18,992 --> 00:12:19,512
Don't worry.

259
00:12:20,153 --> 00:12:21,352
The company will protect them.

260
00:12:21,553 --> 00:12:22,553
Won't affect their jobs.

261
00:12:24,393 --> 00:12:24,893
Okay.

262
00:12:25,752 --> 00:12:26,512
I'll ask around.

263
00:12:28,752 --> 00:12:29,273
Ms. Qi,

264
00:12:31,112 --> 00:12:32,872
does the company have some plan?

265
00:12:33,033 --> 00:12:34,793
It's all because of that Xu Yuntian.

266
00:12:35,512 --> 00:12:36,793
He refuses to resign voluntarily

267
00:12:37,352 --> 00:12:38,712
and he's bargaining.

268
00:12:39,992 --> 00:12:41,433
The company needs to be prepared.

269
00:12:42,512 --> 00:12:43,313
Just in case.

270
00:12:44,992 --> 00:12:46,600
You have so many sales ladies under you.

271
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,752
All of them are beauties.

272
00:12:50,632 --> 00:12:51,432
All hidden dangers.

273
00:12:52,232 --> 00:12:53,512
Alright, it's time.

274
00:12:53,793 --> 00:12:54,752
Go meet the reporters.

275
00:12:55,832 --> 00:12:57,673
Today's goal is to let the public know

276
00:12:57,872 --> 00:12:59,992
that this whole incident
has nothing to do with GST.

277
00:13:00,193 --> 00:13:00,992
Not our fault.

278
00:13:03,433 --> 00:13:04,913
Follow this outline later.

279
00:13:04,953 --> 00:13:05,992
Answer strictly

280
00:13:06,472 --> 00:13:07,816
according to the outline.

281
00:13:09,073 --> 00:13:10,792
They love to poke you for no reason.

282
00:13:11,273 --> 00:13:11,913
And then

283
00:13:12,273 --> 00:13:13,313
make you slip up.

284
00:13:14,352 --> 00:13:16,352
Today's reporters
are our contacts, right?

285
00:13:17,273 --> 00:13:18,352
Still, just in case.

286
00:13:23,592 --> 00:13:25,896
Okay, got it. Let's leave it at that.

287
00:13:27,273 --> 00:13:28,592
(Lv Sa, Famous Journalist)
Sorry for the call.

288
00:13:29,472 --> 00:13:31,352
It's about Xu Yuntian.

289
00:13:33,112 --> 00:13:33,793
What is it?

290
00:13:34,393 --> 00:13:35,033
Some gossip

291
00:13:35,512 --> 00:13:38,024
about him sexually harassing people
several times.

292
00:13:38,232 --> 00:13:41,033
And he's had affairs
with multiple female colleagues.

293
00:13:43,872 --> 00:13:44,712
Let me introduce you.

294
00:13:44,793 --> 00:13:46,752
This is Zhao Mei,
head of Promotions Department.

295
00:13:46,913 --> 00:13:48,232
This is who I mentioned earlier,

296
00:13:48,472 --> 00:13:50,553
the renowned Lv Sa.

297
00:13:50,673 --> 00:13:53,064
- Hello, Ms. Lv. I'm Zhao Mei.
- Nice to meet you.

298
00:13:53,064 --> 00:13:54,112
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to meet you.

299
00:13:54,913 --> 00:13:55,673
Let's get started.

300
00:14:02,232 --> 00:14:03,112
You two go ahead.

301
00:14:04,393 --> 00:14:05,153
I have to go.

302
00:14:17,232 --> 00:14:18,696
How've you been lately?

303
00:14:19,472 --> 00:14:20,232
Going smoothly?

304
00:14:23,992 --> 00:14:24,752
Pretty good.

305
00:14:25,512 --> 00:14:27,472
Nothing's changed from the past.

306
00:14:27,992 --> 00:14:29,153
Work is still just as hectic.

307
00:14:30,752 --> 00:14:31,793
For modern people,

308
00:14:31,992 --> 00:14:33,913
a major warning sign
of a mental breakdown

309
00:14:34,393 --> 00:14:36,273
is believing that work matters most,

310
00:14:36,632 --> 00:14:37,433
yet everything else

311
00:14:38,112 --> 00:14:39,033
isn't worth mentioning.

312
00:14:40,073 --> 00:14:40,793
(What nonsense?)

313
00:14:41,232 --> 00:14:43,193
(Leather jacket, little ponytail,)

314
00:14:43,433 --> 00:14:44,776
(trying to act all edgy with me?)

315
00:14:46,193 --> 00:14:46,793
Hello.

316
00:14:47,632 --> 00:14:48,793
Give me have a lemonade.

317
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,928
Okay, just a moment.

318
00:14:54,033 --> 00:14:54,872
Let's get started.

319
00:15:02,232 --> 00:15:03,112
We can get started.

320
00:15:03,793 --> 00:15:04,632
But

321
00:15:05,472 --> 00:15:07,232
I won't ask questions from the outline.

322
00:15:08,553 --> 00:15:09,673
Prepared Q&A

323
00:15:10,992 --> 00:15:11,953
has no point at all.

324
00:15:14,193 --> 00:15:14,712
Okay.

325
00:15:15,592 --> 00:15:16,273
No problem.

326
00:15:17,673 --> 00:15:19,112
I'll tell you everything I know.

327
00:15:25,193 --> 00:15:26,073
You're very beautiful.

328
00:15:27,872 --> 00:15:28,553
Thank you.

329
00:15:29,592 --> 00:15:30,592
But academically average.

330
00:15:35,153 --> 00:15:36,193
From what I know,

331
00:15:36,553 --> 00:15:37,872
your first job

332
00:15:37,872 --> 00:15:40,153
was as a regular sales lady at GST.

333
00:15:40,793 --> 00:15:42,592
I also read the materials
from your company.

334
00:15:42,752 --> 00:15:44,512
I found that almost all the sales ladies

335
00:15:44,512 --> 00:15:45,953
rise to supervisor level at most.

336
00:15:46,393 --> 00:15:47,112
But you

337
00:15:48,232 --> 00:15:49,472
made it to Deputy Director.

338
00:15:49,832 --> 00:15:50,856
What I want to know now

339
00:15:50,856 --> 00:15:53,153
is how you got
that Deputy Director position.

340
00:16:22,073 --> 00:16:25,673
Anyone who gets promoted
needs their boss's recognition,

341
00:16:26,232 --> 00:16:27,313
support from colleagues,

342
00:16:28,153 --> 00:16:30,232
and their own hard work.

343
00:16:31,632 --> 00:16:33,313
Plus, a little bit of luck.

344
00:16:34,112 --> 00:16:35,553
So, I'm no exception.

345
00:16:37,913 --> 00:16:39,472
The boss's recognition is important.

346
00:16:40,913 --> 00:16:42,273
Could you elaborate

347
00:16:42,913 --> 00:16:44,553
on how your boss helped you?

348
00:16:49,592 --> 00:16:50,712
Ms. Lv,

349
00:16:52,072 --> 00:16:53,160
what do you want to hear?

350
00:16:57,232 --> 00:16:58,712
(I know what you want to hear.)

351
00:16:59,193 --> 00:17:00,992
(Don't you think I got where I am today)

352
00:17:01,232 --> 00:17:02,760
(by sleeping my way up?)

353
00:17:10,913 --> 00:17:11,673
Why not take order?

354
00:17:13,633 --> 00:17:14,272
Troublesome.

355
00:17:16,472 --> 00:17:17,153
Scan a code.

356
00:17:17,752 --> 00:17:19,032
And then pick it up myself.

357
00:17:20,512 --> 00:17:22,072
Now, people have no sense of service.

358
00:17:23,113 --> 00:17:24,913
(Mr. Xu has been
a tremendous help to me.)

359
00:17:25,472 --> 00:17:26,312
I'm very grateful.

360
00:17:27,953 --> 00:17:28,792
Just gratitude?

361
00:17:31,072 --> 00:17:32,232
What else could there be?

362
00:17:32,752 --> 00:17:34,433
But I've also seen quite a few rumors

363
00:17:35,752 --> 00:17:37,752
saying you and Xu Yuntian
have a relationship

364
00:17:37,953 --> 00:17:39,593
that goes beyond professional.

365
00:17:43,792 --> 00:17:45,353
That's all nonsense.

366
00:17:46,153 --> 00:17:47,656
Ms. Lv, a big-shot reporter like you

367
00:17:47,656 --> 00:17:49,113
believes those rumors?

368
00:17:51,593 --> 00:17:53,552
Mr. Xu is my boss,

369
00:17:54,752 --> 00:17:56,392
and we're also good friends.

370
00:17:57,833 --> 00:17:59,368
He was even a witness

371
00:17:59,368 --> 00:18:00,633
at my wedding to my husband.

372
00:18:00,992 --> 00:18:02,193
Your husband doesn't mind?

373
00:18:02,752 --> 00:18:03,873
How's your relationship?

374
00:18:04,153 --> 00:18:05,593
We are good.

375
00:18:07,992 --> 00:18:08,752
Any children?

376
00:18:12,593 --> 00:18:13,393
Ms. Lv,

377
00:18:13,552 --> 00:18:16,153
that's getting a bit personal, isn't it?

378
00:18:17,953 --> 00:18:19,472
Just asking casually. Sorry.

379
00:18:20,472 --> 00:18:21,128
It's fine.

380
00:18:26,032 --> 00:18:26,792
What do you want?

381
00:18:27,752 --> 00:18:28,792
Why not come to my place?

382
00:18:29,272 --> 00:18:31,304
Your wife isn't home.
It wouldn't be proper.

383
00:18:31,673 --> 00:18:32,433
Avoid suspicion?

384
00:18:34,193 --> 00:18:36,673
If you want to avoid suspicion,
why not meet somewhere crowded?

385
00:18:38,312 --> 00:18:39,512
Are you afraid of being seen,

386
00:18:40,072 --> 00:18:41,433
or afraid of me being seen?

387
00:18:42,312 --> 00:18:44,433
I'm afraid of us being seen.

388
00:18:47,992 --> 00:18:49,232
I know why you come see me.

389
00:18:51,072 --> 00:18:52,072
You're worried

390
00:18:52,913 --> 00:18:54,312
that I'll tell others about us.

391
00:18:58,593 --> 00:18:59,093
Mr. Xu.

392
00:19:02,833 --> 00:19:03,353
Mr. Xu.

393
00:19:05,272 --> 00:19:06,552
Don't go home tonight.

394
00:19:19,552 --> 00:19:20,792
Why looking at me like that?

395
00:19:23,153 --> 00:19:24,272
I'm thinking

396
00:19:25,193 --> 00:19:26,752
if I don't go home tonight,

397
00:19:28,272 --> 00:19:29,593
what might happen between us.

398
00:19:30,992 --> 00:19:31,752
What do you think?

399
00:19:33,712 --> 00:19:34,433
What's wrong?

400
00:19:34,992 --> 00:19:37,072
- You have a boyfriend?
- That has nothing to do with it.

401
00:19:37,532 --> 00:19:39,912
I'm thinking if we
really did get involved,

402
00:19:40,593 --> 00:19:42,953
then my expectations
of you would change.

403
00:19:44,113 --> 00:19:44,992
What expectations?

404
00:19:45,193 --> 00:19:46,472
For example, next time,

405
00:19:46,472 --> 00:19:48,512
if sales still don't
take our promotions seriously,

406
00:19:49,232 --> 00:19:50,633
I won't go easy on them.

407
00:19:52,353 --> 00:19:53,272
And Mr. Xu,

408
00:19:54,193 --> 00:19:59,433
you need to publicly
and firmly stand by my side.

409
00:20:06,873 --> 00:20:07,712
Why

410
00:20:10,193 --> 00:20:10,953
sales

411
00:20:12,113 --> 00:20:13,752
wouldn't take promotions seriously?

412
00:20:15,272 --> 00:20:16,113
This isn't right.

413
00:20:19,472 --> 00:20:20,593
(Both you and I know)

414
00:20:21,472 --> 00:20:22,913
(our relationship is crystal clear.)

415
00:20:23,472 --> 00:20:24,552
If you're so confident,

416
00:20:24,992 --> 00:20:27,112
why did you rush here to find me?

417
00:20:27,752 --> 00:20:28,712
Isn't that guilty?

418
00:20:30,113 --> 00:20:31,153
You know I like you.

419
00:20:31,953 --> 00:20:34,593
You rose from a bottom-level sales lady

420
00:20:34,833 --> 00:20:35,953
to your current position

421
00:20:37,232 --> 00:20:38,632
just because of our relationship.

422
00:20:39,673 --> 00:20:40,673
Now that I'm in trouble,

423
00:20:41,393 --> 00:20:42,913
you want to cut ties with me?

424
00:20:43,833 --> 00:20:46,272
This is called ingratitude.

425
00:20:46,272 --> 00:20:46,953
You know?

426
00:20:47,393 --> 00:20:49,833
You're heartless to say these things.

427
00:20:50,472 --> 00:20:52,673
Haven't I done enough for you
over the years?

428
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:54,512
Besides,

429
00:20:54,953 --> 00:20:56,512
I never intended to cut ties with you.

430
00:20:56,833 --> 00:20:57,433
What about you?

431
00:20:57,953 --> 00:20:59,072
What did you do?

432
00:20:59,673 --> 00:21:01,736
You clearly know
how I manage sales ladies

433
00:21:01,736 --> 00:21:02,752
and protect them.

434
00:21:03,393 --> 00:21:04,520
Yet you still harass them.

435
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:05,448
What do you mean?

436
00:21:06,312 --> 00:21:07,153
Enough.

437
00:21:07,953 --> 00:21:09,193
Stop bringing up this mess.

438
00:21:10,593 --> 00:21:11,232
I know

439
00:21:11,913 --> 00:21:13,224
after my scandal,

440
00:21:14,552 --> 00:21:16,272
things haven't been easy for you at GST.

441
00:21:17,072 --> 00:21:18,272
They must give you trouble.

442
00:21:19,752 --> 00:21:21,712
You're job-hunting lately.

443
00:21:22,673 --> 00:21:23,792
Actually, no need to rush.

444
00:21:24,712 --> 00:21:26,216
They can't touch you for now.

445
00:21:27,333 --> 00:21:29,448
- Wait for me...
- I'm not leaving GST.

446
00:21:30,393 --> 00:21:31,953
You still plan to stay at GST?

447
00:21:34,673 --> 00:21:36,168
Then you'll have tough times ahead.

448
00:21:37,153 --> 00:21:39,752
Whether Dong Yue
or Tang Lide replaces me,

449
00:21:39,992 --> 00:21:41,000
they won't trust you.

450
00:21:41,472 --> 00:21:42,512
They'll go with their own.

451
00:21:42,913 --> 00:21:43,953
What if I told you

452
00:21:44,072 --> 00:21:47,232
that I'm the one replacing you
as Sales Director?

453
00:21:50,193 --> 00:21:50,752
You?

454
00:21:55,673 --> 00:21:56,393
Okay.

455
00:21:57,153 --> 00:21:58,593
Just for saying that,

456
00:21:58,913 --> 00:21:59,913
I admire your nerve.

457
00:22:03,593 --> 00:22:04,833
So can you promise me

458
00:22:05,232 --> 00:22:07,472
not to drag me into your war with GST?

459
00:22:09,913 --> 00:22:11,873
If I say yes, would you believe me?

460
00:22:12,393 --> 00:22:13,312
You say it,

461
00:22:14,752 --> 00:22:15,472
and I believe it.

462
00:22:23,913 --> 00:22:24,552
Okay.

463
00:22:25,072 --> 00:22:25,792
I promise you.

464
00:22:27,113 --> 00:22:29,353
I also want your legacy clients.

465
00:22:29,992 --> 00:22:31,353
You're still saying we're clean?

466
00:22:32,393 --> 00:22:33,992
If there's really nothing between us,

467
00:22:34,673 --> 00:22:36,552
how dare you demand things from me?

468
00:22:37,913 --> 00:22:39,913
How can you be so stupid?

469
00:22:40,072 --> 00:22:42,504
- What did you say?
- I said you're stupid.

470
00:22:43,193 --> 00:22:45,593
Listen. You must support me.

471
00:22:46,153 --> 00:22:47,633
If I take your position,

472
00:22:47,633 --> 00:22:48,744
the benefits I can provide

473
00:22:48,744 --> 00:22:50,232
will far exceed what they could.

474
00:22:50,752 --> 00:22:51,833
You're still young,

475
00:22:51,833 --> 00:22:53,913
nowhere near retirement age.

476
00:22:54,072 --> 00:22:55,712
Even if you leave GST,

477
00:22:55,712 --> 00:22:57,552
you'll stay in this industry.

478
00:22:57,833 --> 00:22:59,633
While whether Dong Yue or Tang Lide,

479
00:22:59,633 --> 00:23:02,024
they'll shake you off like a snail

480
00:23:02,024 --> 00:23:03,552
and avoid you like the plague.

481
00:23:04,472 --> 00:23:06,673
Maybe they'll save face in public,

482
00:23:06,673 --> 00:23:07,752
but the next moment,

483
00:23:07,833 --> 00:23:09,992
you'll be the laughingstock
at their drinking parties.

484
00:23:11,472 --> 00:23:12,520
But I

485
00:23:13,552 --> 00:23:15,176
will never laugh at you.

486
00:23:17,128 --> 00:23:17,633
Hello,

487
00:23:19,113 --> 00:23:19,913
your coffee.

488
00:23:22,633 --> 00:23:23,153
Please enjoy.

489
00:23:31,593 --> 00:23:33,312
I can give you all the client lists,

490
00:23:35,153 --> 00:23:37,433
but mark my words.

491
00:23:38,992 --> 00:23:40,584
Even if I give you every list,

492
00:23:41,833 --> 00:23:43,272
you won't become Sales Director.

493
00:23:45,833 --> 00:23:46,472
Why not?

494
00:23:47,072 --> 00:23:48,552
The bosses don't know you.

495
00:23:49,312 --> 00:23:51,552
You've always been
just working under me.

496
00:23:51,712 --> 00:23:53,552
You've never participated in our events.

497
00:23:53,552 --> 00:23:54,248
Of course.

498
00:23:54,472 --> 00:23:55,673
You dislike socializing,

499
00:23:55,873 --> 00:23:57,032
so I never invited you.

500
00:23:58,232 --> 00:23:59,633
But this means

501
00:23:59,633 --> 00:24:01,232
Barry, Peter,

502
00:24:01,873 --> 00:24:02,992
and all management

503
00:24:03,433 --> 00:24:04,833
have no idea who you are.

504
00:24:05,752 --> 00:24:07,784
Why would they promote
someone they don't know?

505
00:24:16,913 --> 00:24:17,864
Sorry about that.

506
00:24:18,873 --> 00:24:20,633
I know it dampened your spirits.

507
00:24:22,712 --> 00:24:23,992
But honestly, I didn't expect

508
00:24:25,312 --> 00:24:27,312
you'd want the Sales Director position.

509
00:24:28,992 --> 00:24:30,633
I'm currently negotiating with GST,

510
00:24:31,593 --> 00:24:33,433
asking for a hefty
severance package from them.

511
00:24:34,913 --> 00:24:35,873
Once this is over,

512
00:24:37,633 --> 00:24:38,593
I'll take you with me.

513
00:24:42,232 --> 00:24:43,912
I won't leave GST.

514
00:24:46,633 --> 00:24:47,673
I'm not going anywhere.

515
00:25:01,472 --> 00:25:03,016
(Even if I give you every list,)

516
00:25:04,312 --> 00:25:05,768
(you won't become Sales Director.)

517
00:25:06,153 --> 00:25:07,624
The bosses don't know you.

518
00:25:08,873 --> 00:25:09,712
(I thought finally)

519
00:25:09,833 --> 00:25:11,312
(I made it to Deputy Director.)

520
00:25:11,393 --> 00:25:13,312
(After all this fuss,
ten years of hard work,)

521
00:25:13,712 --> 00:25:16,584
(I'm still just
a regular sales lady for them.)

522
00:25:23,633 --> 00:25:25,272
This is Ms. Lv's draft article?

523
00:25:27,232 --> 00:25:28,328
She didn't agree to let us review it

524
00:25:28,328 --> 00:25:29,953
before publication, did she?

525
00:25:30,472 --> 00:25:32,032
Don't ask how I got it.

526
00:25:33,232 --> 00:25:35,633
Just tell me what these few lines mean.

527
00:25:36,232 --> 00:25:38,712
What do "The company environment
is extravagant"

528
00:25:39,673 --> 00:25:42,312
and "Sales ladies deal
with a mixed crowd" mean?

529
00:25:43,353 --> 00:25:45,032
I sent you for the interview,

530
00:25:45,312 --> 00:25:47,432
not to represent
the sales ladies' perspective

531
00:25:47,432 --> 00:25:48,648
and criticize the company.

532
00:25:49,256 --> 00:25:51,688
- Ms. Qi, you might have misunderstood.
- Misunderstood what?

533
00:25:51,992 --> 00:25:54,536
This interview draft is not
what the company wanted.

534
00:25:56,992 --> 00:26:00,393
Ms. Lv has the right to decide

535
00:26:00,393 --> 00:26:01,640
how she creates and writes.

536
00:26:02,072 --> 00:26:04,472
She asked me questions,
and I answered truthfully.

537
00:26:05,633 --> 00:26:06,232
Moreover,

538
00:26:06,992 --> 00:26:08,913
I don't see anything wrong
with what she wrote.

539
00:26:10,393 --> 00:26:11,593
That is the biggest problem.

540
00:26:12,353 --> 00:26:14,440
You don't even know what you did wrong?

541
00:26:15,673 --> 00:26:16,392
I know.

542
00:26:16,873 --> 00:26:19,016
You didn't want this interview
from the start.

543
00:26:19,393 --> 00:26:19,893
Fine.

544
00:26:20,913 --> 00:26:22,953
On one hand, you're Xu Yuntian's person.

545
00:26:23,193 --> 00:26:26,184
You're resentful
about Xu Yuntian's departure.

546
00:26:26,633 --> 00:26:29,353
On the other hand,
you want to be the Sales Director.

547
00:26:29,953 --> 00:26:31,953
You're afraid
that once this article comes out,

548
00:26:32,153 --> 00:26:34,353
Promotions Department
will be blamed for the harassment.

549
00:26:35,593 --> 00:26:36,232
I don't know

550
00:26:36,433 --> 00:26:37,913
what you did to Ms. Lv

551
00:26:38,153 --> 00:26:40,673
to get so much praise
for yourself in this draft.

552
00:26:40,953 --> 00:26:41,913
But I'm telling you.

553
00:26:42,232 --> 00:26:45,064
Don't think you can pull
useless little stunts behind my back,

554
00:26:45,272 --> 00:26:46,992
or hold the company back.

555
00:26:48,032 --> 00:26:50,393
Someone like you,
only focused on your own business,

556
00:26:50,393 --> 00:26:51,752
with no big-picture thinking,

557
00:26:52,193 --> 00:26:53,633
the company will never promote you.

558
00:27:11,992 --> 00:27:12,552
Ms. Zhao.

559
00:27:13,593 --> 00:27:14,353
We'll talk later.

560
00:27:17,072 --> 00:27:18,952
(Is that reporter trying to ruin me?)

561
00:27:19,752 --> 00:27:20,252
(No way.)

562
00:27:20,833 --> 00:27:22,696
(I have to find out
what's really going on.)

563
00:27:25,752 --> 00:27:27,312
You don't look happy.

564
00:27:27,593 --> 00:27:29,312
I did speak well of you in the article.

565
00:27:30,552 --> 00:27:31,953
Why did you help me?

566
00:27:33,312 --> 00:27:34,440
During the interview,

567
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:36,752
I could sense you don't like me.

568
00:27:39,992 --> 00:27:40,913
I really didn't.

569
00:27:41,752 --> 00:27:43,353
But I like your ambition.

570
00:27:45,752 --> 00:27:46,552
Ambition?

571
00:27:47,633 --> 00:27:49,433
Don't you always want
to be Sales Director?

572
00:27:50,552 --> 00:27:52,872
As far as I know,
in the entire liquor industry,

573
00:27:53,072 --> 00:27:55,113
