to cause you trouble.

587
00:28:31,792 --> 00:28:32,712
I really appreciate it.

588
00:28:34,673 --> 00:28:35,752
I like your article.

589
00:28:38,232 --> 00:28:38,792
It's a shame.

590
00:28:38,953 --> 00:28:40,792
