won't get published now.

591
00:28:42,472 --> 00:28:44,072
So, what are you going to do next?

592
00:28:46,992 --> 00:28:48,072
I don't know.

593
00:28:48,312 --> 00:28:50,792
These past few days,
I've gone over it countless times.

594
00:28:50,873 --> 00:28:52,433
I don't see anything I did wrong.

595
00:28:52,953 --> 00:28:54,193
If it's not you,

596
00:28:55,512 --> 00:28:57,000
