597
00:28:57,752 --> 00:28:59,912
Since you know
where the problem lies now,

598
00:29:00,512 --> 00:29:02,408
you should be the one to change it,

599
00:29:03,433 --> 00:29:04,872
instead of covering it up for them.

600
00:29:07,848 --> 00:29:14,472
(Sunshine Observer Magazine,
Insight Media Co., Ltd.)

601
00:29:16,673 --> 00:29:17,752
You're egging me on?

602
00:29:19,353 --> 00:29:20,913
You can't bear to lose that article.

603
00:29:22,752 --> 00:29:25,433
