is unfair to women.

605
00:29:28,913 --> 00:29:29,752
Good luck.

606
00:29:43,193 --> 00:29:44,584
(If it's not you,)

607
00:29:45,448 --> 00:29:46,992
(it's the company that has a problem.)

608
00:29:47,193 --> 00:29:48,433
How could the company be wrong?

609
00:29:49,433 --> 00:29:51,153
A company is an institution.

610
00:29:51,472 --> 00:29:52,792
It can't make mistakes.

611
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:55,433
(So the biggest mistake
lies with Zhao Mei's mishandling.)

612
00:29:55,913 --> 00:29:57,832
If Zeng Zixuan hadn't been fired,

613
00:29:57,832 --> 00:29:59,633
