624
00:30:24,153 --> 00:30:26,312
(Since you know
where the problem lies now,)

625
00:30:27,072 --> 00:30:28,833
you should be the one to change it,

626
00:30:29,928 --> 00:30:31,368
instead of covering it up for them.

627
00:30:32,353 --> 00:30:34,856
(They all think I'm pushover,)

628
00:30:34,953 --> 00:30:37,160
(using me like a rag
and tossing me aside.)

629
00:30:37,593 --> 00:30:39,552
(I grew up in the seafood
wholesale market.)

630
00:30:39,552 --> 00:30:41,272
(You think I'm scared
of cowards like you?)

631
00:30:42,552 --> 00:30:44,552
(You think I wasted these ten years?)

632
00:30:45,873 --> 00:30:47,272
(You won't let me live.)

633
00:30:47,633 --> 00:30:49,288
(Then I won't let you live easy.)

634
00:30:49,992 --> 00:30:51,353
(Don't know who I am, huh?)

635
00:30:51,633 --> 00:30:52,133
(Fine.)

636
00:30:52,633 --> 00:30:55,833
(Then I'll make sure you know me well.)

637
00:31:01,312 --> 00:31:02,712
