674
00:32:38,593 --> 00:32:40,040
Because we're in nightclubs.

675
00:32:40,040 --> 00:32:41,320
Because we're beautiful.

676
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:42,856
Because customers have no shame.

677
00:32:49,913 --> 00:32:51,552
Can we then conclude

678
00:32:52,712 --> 00:32:56,113
