I heard that.

693
00:33:40,552 --> 00:33:41,633
Then whose fault is it?

694
00:33:42,248 --> 00:33:43,633
Whose fault?

695
00:33:44,873 --> 00:33:45,712
Whose fault?

696
00:33:50,193 --> 00:33:51,153
