715
00:34:46,672 --> 00:34:47,552
I'm sorry.

716
00:34:59,833 --> 00:35:00,648
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

717
00:35:00,712 --> 00:35:01,613
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

718
00:35:02,072 --> 00:35:02,753
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

719
00:35:03,032 --> 00:35:05,313
- Ms. Zhao, you're awesome!
- Awesome!

720
00:35:05,313 --> 00:35:06,233
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

721
00:35:06,233 --> 00:35:06,992
Thank you.

722
00:35:06,992 --> 00:35:07,688
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

723
00:35:07,688 --> 00:35:08,313
Bravo!

724
00:35:08,456 --> 00:35:09,352
Thank you, Ms. Zhao!

725
00:35:10,192 --> 00:35:11,353
